Text:
PS: I personally don't have used this compression enough to have an opinion on it, so I can't recommend it in any way for any mixing or mastering purpose.
However this is a clean and fully functional release that I've uploaded and tested on a request of a TPB user. So your comments are welcome to clarify the quality of this software.
With much much love, Akun.

If downtime of the torrent occurs that's my pretty old seedbox which is probably doing fun stuff.
I have an eye on it so you may be patient ;)
